%% OpenVINO Model Server - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServeProxy as KServe Proxy<br/>(kube-rbac-proxy)
    participant gRPC as OVMS gRPC Listener<br/>8085/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant REST as OVMS REST Listener<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/1.1
    participant Handler as REST API Handler<br/>(Route Dispatcher)
    participant TFS as TFS Frontend<br/>(v1 API)
    participant KFS as KFS Frontend<br/>(v2 API)
    participant MediaPipe as MediaPipe Graph<br/>(v3 GenAI API)
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime
    participant S3 as S3/GCS/Azure<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: gRPC Model Inference (TFS/KServe V2)
    Client->>KServeProxy: gRPC Request<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KServeProxy->>gRPC: Forward (plaintext)<br/>PredictionService.Predict / GRPCInferenceService.ModelInfer
    gRPC->>OV: C++ API call<br/>In-process inference
    OV-->>gRPC: Inference Result
    gRPC-->>KServeProxy: gRPC Response
    KServeProxy-->>Client: Prediction Result

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: REST Inference (OpenAI-compatible v3)
    Client->>KServeProxy: POST /v3/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KServeProxy->>REST: Forward (plaintext)
    REST->>Handler: Route request
    Handler->>MediaPipe: OpenAI chat completion
    MediaPipe->>OV: GenAI Pipeline<br/>Tokenize + Inference + Decode
    OV-->>MediaPipe: Generated tokens
    MediaPipe-->>Handler: Completion response
    Handler-->>REST: JSON/SSE response
    REST-->>KServeProxy: HTTP Response (streaming SSE supported)
    KServeProxy-->>Client: Chat completion

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Model Loading from Remote Storage
    Note right of gRPC: On startup or config reload
    gRPC->>S3: HTTPS/443<br/>AWS IAM / GCP SA / Azure creds
    S3-->>gRPC: Model artifacts
    gRPC->>OV: Load model<br/>C++ API (model load)
    OV-->>gRPC: Model ready

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: REST Model Inference (KServe V2)
    Client->>KServeProxy: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer
    KServeProxy->>REST: Forward (plaintext)
    REST->>Handler: Route request
    Handler->>KFS: KServe V2 inference
    KFS->>OV: C++ API inference
    OV-->>KFS: Result
    KFS-->>Handler: Response
    Handler-->>REST: JSON response
    REST-->>KServeProxy: HTTP Response
    KServeProxy-->>Client: Inference result
